  - id: 3635
    name: D4
    description: "T\xF2a D4 t\u1EA1i \u0110\u1EA1i h\u1ECDc B\xE1ch khoa H\xE0 N\u1ED9i
      l\xE0 tr\u1EE5 s\u1EDF ch\xEDnh c\u1EE7a Tr\u01B0\u1EDDng Ngo\u1EA1i ng\u1EEF
      (tr\u01B0\u1EDBc \u0111\xE2y l\xE0 Khoa Ngo\u1EA1i ng\u1EEF). \u0110\xE2y l\xE0
      \u0111\u1ECBa \u0111i\u1EC3m quen thu\u1ED9c v\u1EDBi sinh vi\xEAn B\xE1ch
      khoa, \u0111\u1EB7c bi\u1EC7t l\xE0 trong c\xE1c k\u1EF3 thi ti\u1EBFng Anh
      v\xE0 c\xE1c ho\u1EA1t \u0111\u1ED9ng h\u1ECDc t\u1EADp ng\xF4n ng\u1EEF"
