  - id: 3265
    name: C4
    description: "T\xF2a C4 t\u1EA1i Tr\u01B0\u1EDDng \u0110\u1EA1i h\u1ECDc B\xE1ch
      khoa H\xE0 N\u1ED9i l\xE0 tr\u1EE5 s\u1EDF c\u1EE7a Vi\u1EC7n C\xF4ng ngh\u1EC7
      Sinh h\u1ECDc v\xE0 C\xF4ng ngh\u1EC7 Th\u1EF1c ph\u1EA9m (SBFT), n\u1EB1m
      trong khu\xF4n vi\xEAn tr\u01B0\u1EDDng. \u0110\xE2y l\xE0 n\u01A1i l\xE0m
      vi\u1EC7c, gi\u1EA3ng d\u1EA1y v\xE0 nghi\xEAn c\u1EE9u ch\xEDnh c\u1EE7a vi\u1EC7n,
      th\u01B0\u1EDDng bao g\u1ED3m c\xE1c v\u0103n ph\xF2ng khoa, ph\xF2ng l\xE0m
      vi\u1EC7c c\u1EE7a gi\u1EA3ng vi\xEAn v\xE0 c\xE1c ph\xF2ng th\xED nghi\u1EC7m
      chuy\xEAn ng\xE0nh. "
