  - id: 2496
    name: C1
    description: "t\xF2a nh\xE0 C1 \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c bi\u1EBFt \u0111\u1EBFn l\xE0
      m\u1ED9t trong nh\u1EEFng c\xF4ng tr\xECnh ki\u1EBFn tr\xFAc tr\u1ECDng \u0111i\u1EC3m
      c\u1EE7a tr\u01B0\u1EDDng, do c\xE1c k\u0129 s\u01B0 Li\xEAn X\xF4 qua Vi\u1EC7t
      Nam h\u1ED7 tr\u1EE3 v\xE0 x\xE2y d\u1EF1ng. Hi\u1EC7n nay, t\xF2a C1 \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c
      s\u1EED d\u1EE5ng l\xE0m trung t\xE2m v\u0103n ph\xF2ng v\xE0 qu\u1EA3n tr\u1ECB
      c\u1EE7a to\xE0n b\u1ED9 nh\xE0 tr\u01B0\u1EDDng."
